### Friends CRUD
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Create friend
POST {{baseUrl}}/friends
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "name": "John"
}

### List friends
GET {{baseUrl}}/friends
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get friend by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/friends/{{friendId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update friend
PUT {{baseUrl}}/friends/{{friendId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### Delete friend
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/friends/{{friendId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
